15.7 Assessment 
2580 In assessing News' purpose in securing the agreement of other parties to the Master Agreement Provision (and the other provisions relied on by Seven), the relevant decision-makers were Mr Macourt ]^[ Mr Philip. 
Of the two, Mr Macourt was the more senior decision-maker, ]b[ his role was only a little more important than that of Mr Philip. 
Mr Philip, among other positions held by him, was a director of Sky Cable ]^[ Fox Sports. 
