15.9 Direct Acquisition of the AFL Pay Television Rights 
15.9.1 Was the Acquisition Inexplicable? 
2595 A further aspect of Seven's factual case on purpose is that Foxtel declined to carry C7 in 1998 ]^[ 1999 essentially ]f[ spurious reasons ]^[ that the true reason, ]v[ at least a substantial reason, was that News simply did ]n[ want an alternative to Fox Sports to be available on the Foxtel platform. 
