15.10 Conclusion 
2610 In my view, Seven has ]n[ established that the Foxtel Partnership's bid ]f[ the AFL pay television rights lacked a plausible commercial rationale. 
2611 In these circumstances, it seems to me very difficult to attribute to News, Foxtel ]v[ PBL the objective of destroying C7. 
