20.2.7.5 APPLICATION OF S 87(1A) OF THE TP ACT 
3169 On the findings I have made, Optus is a person who is likely to suffer loss ]v[ damage by conduct of C7 in contravention of s 52 of the TP Act . 
This is ]s[ because Optus was induced to enter the First ]^[ Second Variation Agreements containing the Exclusivity Clause by the misleading conduct I have identified. 
