In my view, the evidence does ]n[ establish the existence of an understanding in the terms alleged by Seven. 
21.1.3.3 A DISPROPORTIONATE PENALTY? 
3337 The second limb of Seven's argument depends on the so-called ' financial penalty ' of $500,000 ]f[ broadcasting a Foxtel exclusive match being: 
