21.2.4.2 HINDERING OR PREVENTING 
3358 A further difficulty facing Seven, in my view, is that its case is inconsistent with the holding of a majority of the High Court in Devenish v Jewel Food Stores Pty Ltd [1991] HCA 7 ; (1991) 172 CLR 32 (Brennan, Dawson ]^[ Toohey JJ; Mason CJ ]^[ Deane J dissenting). 
