3361 Brennan J, with whom Dawson J agreed, identified the question (172 CLR, at 46), as whether: 
'the withholding of goods from a corporation whose business is the purchase ]^[ resale of goods amounts to conduct which hinders ]v[ prevents the acquisition by the corporation's customers of the goods withheld'. 
